text: Vlad Cotuna (born 4 November 1990) is a Romanian gymnast. He competed in five events at the 2012 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Romania Category:Gymnasts at the 2012 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Timișoara Category:European Games competitors for Romania Category:Gymnasts at the 2015 European Games
